edu.mines.jtk.mesh

Interface TriMesh.NodePropertyMap

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Enclosing class:
    TriMesh

    public static interface TriMesh.NodePropertyMap
extends java.io.Serializable
    Implemented by maps that associate property values with mesh nodes. This interface is implemented by all node property maps created by this mesh. However, other implementations are possible.
